---
import AppLayout from '../../layouts/AppLayout.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<AppLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — SecureDiary"
  description="SecureDiary privacy policy. We collect zero data. Your diary entries never leave your device."
  appName="SecureDiary"
>
  <section class="privacy">
    <div class="privacy__inner">
      <h1>SecureDiary Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="privacy__date">Last updated: April 19, 2026</p>

      <h2>Summary</h2>
      <p>SecureDiary does not collect, store, transmit, or share any of your personal data. Your diary entries, photos, and settings never leave your device. There are no servers, no analytics, no ads, and no tracking of any kind.</p>

      <h2>Data Storage</h2>
      <p>All data is stored locally on your device:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Diary entries and photos</strong> are encrypted using AES-256-GCM and stored in a SQLCipher-encrypted database on your device.</li>
        <li><strong>Your encryption key</strong> is derived from your PIN and stored in your device's hardware-backed keystore.</li>
        <li><strong>Biometric data</strong> is handled entirely by your device's operating system. SecureDiary never accesses or stores biometric data directly.</li>
        <li><strong>App settings</strong> (theme, reminder time, prompt preferences) are stored locally.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Collection</h2>
      <p>SecureDiary collects <strong>no data whatsoever</strong>. Specifically:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>No personal information</li>
        <li>No usage analytics or telemetry</li>
        <li>No crash reports sent externally</li>
        <li>No advertising identifiers</li>
        <li>No device identifiers</li>
        <li>No location data</li>
        <li>No cookies or tracking</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Network Access</h2>
      <p>SecureDiary does not request or use internet permissions. The app functions entirely offline and makes zero network connections.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>SecureDiary does not integrate with any third-party services, SDKs, or APIs. There are no analytics providers, ad networks, or social media integrations.</p>

      <h2>Data Deletion</h2>
      <p>Uninstalling SecureDiary permanently deletes all app data from your device. You can also delete individual entries or all data from within the app.</p>

      <h2>Data Recovery</h2>
      <p>Because your data is encrypted with your PIN and never transmitted anywhere, there is no way to recover your data if you forget your PIN and lose biometric access. This is intentional — true privacy means no backdoors, not even for us.</p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>SecureDiary does not knowingly collect any data from anyone, including children under 13. Since no data is collected or transmitted, COPPA compliance is inherent to the app's design.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>If this privacy policy is updated, changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. Since SecureDiary collects no data, significant changes are unlikely.</p>

      <div class="privacy__contact">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact us at:<br />
        <strong>inkwellstudio38@gmail.com</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer extraLinks={[{ label: 'Back to SecureDiary', href: '/diary' }]} />
</AppLayout>

<style>
  .privacy {
    padding: 120px 0 var(--section-padding);
  }

  .privacy__inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .privacy__inner h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .privacy__date {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .privacy__inner h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .privacy__inner p {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .privacy__inner ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    list-style: disc;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .privacy__inner li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .privacy__contact {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #f5efe8;
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  }

  .privacy__contact h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
</style>
